<div class="content">
    <div class="container faq-text">
        <div class="text-center">
            <h1 class="mt-5 text-center text-bold content-title d-inline-block">Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)</h1>
            <div class="mt-2 mb-5 text-center">Updated 24 March 2022</div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4 mb-5">
                <div class="nav flex-column nav-pills" id="v-pills-tab" role="tablist" aria-orientation="vertical">
                    <a class="nav-link active" id="v-pills-home-tab" data-toggle="pill" href="#v-pills-home" role="tab" aria-controls="v-pills-home" aria-selected="true">Account and Profile</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" id="v-pills-profile-tab" data-toggle="pill" href="#v-pills-profile" role="tab" aria-controls="v-pills-profile" aria-selected="false">Buying on Shuq</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" id="v-pills-messages-tab" data-toggle="pill" href="#v-pills-messages" role="tab" aria-controls="v-pills-messages" aria-selected="false">Selling on Shuq</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" id="v-pills-settings-tab" data-toggle="pill" href="#v-pills-settings" role="tab" aria-controls="v-pills-settings" aria-selected="false">Shipping and Delivery</a>
                    <a class="nav-link" id="v-pills-discounts-tab" data-toggle="pill" href="#v-pills-discounts" role="tab" aria-controls="v-pills-discounts" aria-selected="false">Discounts</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="tab-content" id="v-pills-tabContent">
                    <div class="tab-pane fade show active" id="v-pills-home" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="v-pills-home-tab">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-sm-12">
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    How do I get started?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    Click on ‘Sign Up’, then create an account with your email address. To setup your profile, go to ‘Create Profile’ and enter your details in the fields, then click ‘Submit’.
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    How do I edit my profile?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    Go to 'Edit' and modify the fields your details as required, then click 'Submit'.
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    What if I forgot my password?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    Click on 'Forgot password' and a link would be sent to your email to reset the password.
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    Can I set my account status as offline / online?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    Yes, after logging in, go to Account, then select 'Offline'. By going Offline, your profile will not be searchable or viewable by other users. Click on the link and follow the instructions.
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    Do I need to pay to setup an account?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    No, registration is free  which means you do not need to pay anything to setup an account.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="v-pills-profile" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="v-pills-profile-tab">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-sm-12">
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    What’s Shuq all about?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    Shuq caters to the cottage industry; our target sellers are individuals or families who are excellent in cooking, baking, sewing, painting and an endless list of skills and talents.
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    What products do you offer on Shuq?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    Yadiyad Shuq is a platform for homemade food and handmade items made by individuals and families. Generally there are two major categories of products: perishable (warm, frozen, storable) and non-perishable (non-food). There are two sections: Shuq Eats which caters for warm and frozen food whilst Shuq Mart offers storable food and non-perishable items.
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    What’s the difference between Shuq Eats and Shuq Mart?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    There are two major differences of Shuq Eats and Shuq Mart; the type of products sold and the method of delivery. On Shuq Eats, you can order homemade warm or frozen foods near your neighbourhood and these will be delivered to you by our despatch riders. On Shuq Mart, you can order handmade items such as bags, trinkets etc.
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    What payment option do you accept?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    We accept the following payment options: FPX (online banking) and eWallets (Boost, Touch n Go, GrabPay, Maybank QR, MCash and Shopee Pay).
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    Can I return or seek for refund for the purchased item?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    Return is only allowed for non-perishable (non-food) items and provided the terms and conditions for return are met. Please refer to Return and Refund policy for more information.
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    How do I provide feedback regarding the product I purchased?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    Click on ‘Feedbacks’ to provide your review or feedback specific to the product and your purchase experience. Comments are subjected to our ‘Terms of Service’ policy.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="v-pills-discounts" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="v-pills-discounts-tab">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-sm-12">
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    Are there any discounts on Yadiyad?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    Yes, from time to time you will enjoy discounts off individual products, shipping fees or the total purchase amount. 
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    What are the available discounts on Yadiyad?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    <span>There are discounts provided by Sellers and Yadiyad:</span>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li class="mb-3">1) Discounts provided by the Sellers are shown on the bottom of the Seller’s products section highlighted in red.</li>
                                        <li class="mb-3"><img src="/img/shuq/faq/vendor_discount.png" alt="" width="779" height="372"></li>
                                        <li class="mb-3">2) Discounts provided by Yadiyad are shown at the bottom of the Total Summary section highlighted in red.</li>
                                        <li class="mb-3"><img src="/img/shuq/faq/platform_discount.png" alt="" width="779" height="372"></li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    How do I redeem the discounts?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    The discounts will be automatically calculated by Yadiyad when you check out and deducted from the product price or shipping fee or total purchase (where applicable) before you make the final payment. You do not need to enter any discount codes.
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    I see discounts from both Yadiyad and Seller. Will I enjoy the discounts from Seller and Yadiyad at the same time?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    No, if there are discounts from Seller and Yadiyad, only the Seller’s discount applies.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="v-pills-messages" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="v-pills-messages-tab">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-sm-12">
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    Why sell on Shuq?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    Shuq offers:
                                    <ul>
                                        <li class="mb-3">Free and easy listing – Registration is free and sellers can create their profile and list their products for free</li>
                                        <li class="mb-3">Payment – Payment is made on Shuq, taking away the hassle of manually tracking each payment from random buyers and it also gives the seller privacy</li>
                                        <li class="mb-3">Shipping – We work with our logistic partners so that sellers do not need to look for their own shipping company. Sellers would only need to pack their items accordingly and either despatch them to riders or drop them off at collection points.</li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    What if I want to sell both perishable and non-perishable products?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    That’s definitely possible and to do that you would need to create your shop profile and product listing separately on both Shuq Eats and Shuq Mart.
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    How and when do I get paid after a sales?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    You will receive payment minus any applicable service charges via online transfer to your bank account. Our payment cycle is on the 7th, 14th, 21st and 28th of every month.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="tab-pane fade" id="v-pills-settings" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="v-pills-settings-tab">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-sm-12">
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    How does Yadiyad arrange for delivery?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    Basically we use two types of delivery: despatch and courier.
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    Can I choose my preferred delivery slot?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    Delivery slots are only available for warm and frozen perishable items.
                                </div>
                                <div class="text-bold mb-2">
                                    How can I know the coverage area?
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-5">
                                    On Shuq Eats, key in your address postcode and the items available within your coverage area will be displayed.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>



    </div>
</div>



